    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a pretty strong take. You're saying they're basically just a tax? What about the argument that they help bring manufacturing back to our country and reduce reliance on foreign powers? Doesn't that have some value for national security?",
      "source": "evaluator",
